How to Automate Tasks Using Python?
Identify the Task. Identify the task that you want to automate. ...
Break Down the Task. Break down the task into smaller subtasks that can be automated using Python. ...
Research. ...
Write the Code. ...
Test the Code. ...
Run the Code. ...
Monitor and Update.
